To build the project, navigate to the M4 directory and run:

	ant clean && ant

[INFO] Please start ECS first, and ensure ECS does not crash/is the last program to exit

To start ECS:

	java -jar m4-ecs.jar -a <ECSip> -p <ECSport>

	To see all the available flags, run java -jar m4-ecs.jar



To start a KVServer:

	java -jar m4-server.jar -b <ECSip:ECSport> -p <serverPort> -d <nameofdirectorytostorekeys>

	To see all the available flags, run java -jar m4-server.jar



To start a KVClient:

	java -jar m4-client.jar

	For usage, see the "help" command